description: Global Logistics Supply Chain Job Board
overview: Global Supply Chain Jobs is an Employment Board designed to cater the needs of Logistics & Supply Chain community around the world. The scope of Global Supply Chain Jobs includes all aspects of Supply Chain which include Procurement/Purchasing, Manufacutring, Transportation and Warehousing. In addition we list jobs related to various support functions such as Information Technology, Sales, Finance, Human Resources and other functions in the context of Supply Chain Management. This service is completely free to Job Seekers.
